{"tid":531493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港人)脫亞入歐,續領BNO,根絕大中華思想!","createTime":"2018-01-17T01:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T04:02:59.000Z","uid":108610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3cb82a513f73f746ff9d60512af25b16b6e0239","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"由於福澤諭吉基於優勝劣汰的思想，認定東方文明必定失敗，因此他呼籲與東亞鄰國絕交，避免<del>日本</del>香港被西方視為與鄰國同樣的「野蠻」之地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「為今之謀，不可再有等待鄰國文明共興亞細亞之猶豫， 不如脫離其伍與西洋文明共進退。 」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">脫亞入歐,與東亞鄰國絕交</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c471c55f26e133b3462e9b5894901a0321c83de9","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"　雖然我<del>日本</del>香港之國位於亞細亞<del>東部</del>南部，但國民的精神已經開始脫離亞細亞的頑固守舊，向西洋文明轉移。然而不幸的是在近鄰有兩個國家，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個叫支那（這裡的支那指中國－－譯者注）</span></span>，一個叫朝鮮。這兩國的人民，自古以來受亞細亞式的政教風俗所熏陶，這與我<del>日本</del>香港國並無不同。也許是因為人種的由來有所不同，也許是儘管大家都處於同樣的政教風俗之中，但在遺傳教育方面卻有不盡相同之處。<del>日</del>港、支、韓三國相對而言，與<del>日本</del>香港相比，支國與韓國的相似之處更為接近。這兩個國家一樣，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不管是個人還是國家，都不思改進之道。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dfd40ebda5e5d21de37f5b58c98bba5c0b943c5","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"假如支那、朝鮮政府的陳舊專制體制無法律可依，西洋人就懷疑<del>日本</del>香港也是無法律的國家；假如支那、朝鮮的知識人自我沉溺不知科學為何物，西洋人就認為<del>日本</del>香港也是陰陽五行的國家；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">假如支那人卑屈不知廉恥</span></span>，<del>日本</del>香港人的俠義就會因此被掩蓋；假如朝鮮國對人使用酷刑，<del>日本</del>香港人就會被推測也是同樣的沒有人性。如此事例，不勝枚舉。"},{"pid":"c3f9318dc0f019fa3015eb1815c26be3d60cc199","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"　打個比方，屋院相鄰的村莊內的一群人，在他們出現無法無天的愚行而且殘酷無情的時候，即使這個村莊裡偶爾有一家人注意品行的端正，也會被他人的醜行所淹沒。和這個例子一樣，支、韓兩國的影響已成為既成的事實，間接地對我外交產生了障礙，這樣的事情實際上並不少，可以說這是我<del>日本</del>香港國的一大不幸。"},{"pid":"c477c5db0c1aadc5be042aa23a9976ffada3e548","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:51:07.000Z","msg":"既然如此，作為當今之策，我國不應猶豫，與其坐等鄰國的開明，共同振興亞洲，不如脫離其行列，而與西洋文明國共進退。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對待支那、朝鮮的方法，也不必因其為鄰國而特別予以同情，只要模仿西洋人對他們的態度方式對付即可。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">與壞朋友親近的人也難免近墨者黑，我們要從內心謝絕亞細亞東方的壞朋友。</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f2c31d16c41f542089f60595deec29e97b0dc4e","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6921c5054ceb2a8ef77d1acafb8969064e8dae39","tid":531493,"uid":108610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}